data.description:
Absolutely stunning! This meticulously updated 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home boasts over 4000 square feet of finished living space and is situated on a sprawling 3.48-acre lot. The attention to detail is evident throughout, making it a true standout in the market.

Step inside to discover a home that seamlessly blends modern luxury with timeless charm. Gleaming hardwood floors flow throughout the main level, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The spacious and well-appointed kitchen is perfect for entertaining guests or preparing family meals.

The expansive living areas are bathed in natural light, creating an open and airy feel. The four bedrooms, including a lavish master suite, offer ample space and privacy for the entire family. Each bathroom has been thoughtfully updated, showcasing the latest in design trends and high-end finishes.

The finished lower level adds another dimension to this home, providing additional space for recreation, a home office, or a media room - the possibilities are endless. With over 4000 square feet, there's room for everyone to live, work, and play comfortably.

Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the vast 3.48-acre lot, offering a private and serene setting. Whether you're enjoying a quiet morning coffee on the deck or hosting a summer barbecue, this property provides the perfect backdrop for outdoor living.

Convenience meets luxury with the attached 3-car garage, ensuring ample space for vehicles and storage. Located in the sought-after Williamston school district, this home offers not just a residence but a lifestyle.

Don't miss the opportunity to call this exceptional property your home. Schedule your private tour today and experience the epitome of refined living in a prime real estate location.
